SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4790
A bill to amend 1978 PA 368, entitled
"Public health code,"
by amending sections 17033 and 17533 (MCL 333.17033 and 333.17533),
as amended by 1994 PA 234.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 17033. (1) Notwithstanding the requirements of part 161,
2 the board may require a licensee physician seeking renewal of a
3 license to furnish the board with satisfactory evidence that during
4 the 3 years immediately preceding application for renewal the
5 licensee physician has attended continuing education courses or
6 programs approved by the board totaling not less than 150 hours in
7 subjects related to the practice of medicine including, but not
8 limited to, medical ethics and designed to further educate
